node.text: Some of you may be getting ready to leave your pet with a dogsitter while you travel or head back to the office. Before you do, don’t forget to set up your smart home devices and @alexa99 Routines so you can keep up your pets during the transition. Having my Alexa Routines set up and being able to talk to my pets through the Blink Home Monitor App has been a game changer for me when I have long days at the office. @Amazon @BlinkForHome #AskAlexa #ad
